title: Windows XP Pro SP3 [CORP] 32-bit ENU
description:
W007 my first torrent. But don&#039;t let that scare you, I made this one myself. ;)
I&#039;ve slipstreamed the latest (Release) Service Pack 3 onto my corporate WinXP disc and burnt whole with Nero. 
Mind you, this is the english version. (I Don&#039;t believe many other languages SP3-Release are available yet...)

On the CD you&#039;ll find a text file named: serial.txt it is there where you can find you product key. 

THIS VERSION NEEDS NO WINDOWS PRODUCT ACTIVATION !

(but it doesn&#039;t pass the genuine validation either ;-) )

Please SHARE with everyone, cause I&#039;m doing this from a semi-public PC and can&#039;t keep it on too long (max 12 hours per day)
